high_descs: Turn to your left and go to face the counter between the two sinks.
Pick up the spray bottle closest to the front edge of the counter.
Go left to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle in the gray bin to the right of the toilet.
Turn right and return to the counter between the sinks.
Pick up the remaining purple spray bottle.
Go left, back to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle into the gray bin with the other spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles from a bathroom sink to a waste bin.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk towards the wall until you reach the empty counter space between the two bathroom sinks, on your right, turn to your right and go to the counter space.
Pick up the purple spray bottle closest to the edge of the counter.
Turn to your left and walk to the small space between the bathroom counter and the toilet, where the garbage can is, to your right.
Place the purple spray bottle in the toilet.
Turn to your right and go back to the empty counter space in between the two sinks.
Pick up the purple spray bottle, behind the nail polish, on the counter.
Turn to your left and walk back to the garbage can, on the floor, between the counter and the toilet, on your right.
Place the purple spray bottle in the garbage can to the right of the other one.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles in the garbage can.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter between the sinks
Grab a spray bottle on the counter
Turn left and go to the trash can
Put the bottle in the trash can
Turn left and go to the counter between the sinks
Grab a spray bottle off of the counter
Turn right and go to the trash can
Put the bottle in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Putting two spray bottles in the trash can
